CORPHISH were originally foreign
POKMON that were imported as pets.
They eventually turned up in the wild. This POKMON is very hardy and has
greatly increased its population.

claws. It has no likes or dislikes when it
comes to food - it will eat anything. This POKMON has no trouble living in
filthy water.

Once it grips prey with its large pincers,
it will never let go, no matter what.
It is a hardy POKMON that can thrive
in any environment.
